profile:
Waste Less Recycling and Diversion Inc is a not-for-profit social enterprise focused on reducing waste sent to landfill by offering affordable junk removal services for the Kingston area. We are a polite, fast and courteous group offering fast CONTACT-LESS removal of your junk.


We are also fully insured and registered with the Ministry of the Environment.  Waste Less is the responsible, trustworthy choice for YOUR junk removal job. Call or text us now! 343-333-4028
